text: Fiction Non-Fiction is the fourth album by Danish Industrial band Psychopomps. ==Track listing== *Track 9 is a cover of a Velvet Underground song written by Lou Reed ==Personnel== *Jesper Schmidt: Vox, Programming, Keyboards *Flemming Norre Larsen: Programming, Lyrics *Kaare Mogensen: Guitars ==External links== * Psychopomps at myspace Category:1997 albums Category:Psychopomps (band) albums
title: Fiction Non-Fiction
